**Metrics**:
- Model accuracy, F1, MAE (convergence quality)
- Detection precision, recall, F1 (Byzantine identification)
- MTTR = Mean Time To Recovery (rounds until accuracy recovers)
- Evasion rate = % Byzantine clients escaping detection
- Aggregation time, communication overhead

**Statistical Rigor**: 10 random seeds, Wilcoxon signed-rank test (p<0.05), 95% confidence intervals, ANOVA

